name: MORK
description: Mork is a meme coin powered by a green cartoon dog with questionable intentions and a surprising grasp of blockchain fundamentals. It lives on the Solana network, where transactions are faster, fees are lower, and weirdness is welcomed. The project doesn’t promise utility-laced moon missions—it delivers community-driven chaos, meme culture, and a green dog who probably shouldn’t have this much influence. It’s meme meets machine, and somehow it works.
